Jesse found his voice through collaborations with artists and producers in Mexico. ´No Eres tú´ is his latest single feat. C.tangana, and it hit 4 million views in just a couple of months. A few releases later he found himself signed with UME sub-label Broke Kids. Read more on Last.fm

Jhay Cortez (9 de abril de 1993) cantante y compositor del género urbano. Nació en Río Piedras, Puerto Rico. Su nombre de nacimiento es Jesús Manuel Nieves Cortez. Sus numerosas colaboraciones con importantes exponentes del género le han permitido demostrar su talento y ganar respeto dentro de la escena artística.May 24, 2019 Read more on Last.fm

Easy Easy is a Guatemalan four piece band formed by Walter Monterroso ( Keyboard and Bass), Sofía Insua (Vocals), Gerardo Flores (Drums) and Rodolfo Madrid (Guitar). The group strives to combine different influences such as R&B, Pop, Hip Hop and Indie Rock, while also playing with languages - English and Spanish - resulting in a very unique alternative sound.
